summary: Sunsprite TGA + Settings + PSD-ressource for Frazetta ENB - Human Temporal Glare Sunsprite at http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/61405/?
descriptionHtml:
Sunsprite TGA + Settings + PSD-ressource for "Frazetta ENB - Human Temporal Glare Sunsprite"

The Frazetta-ENB-Mod could be found at http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/61405/? is needed to get
the sunsprite from my mod to work.

This is for testing purposal, and for all who are interested in, it's for supporting Veeblix and Kingeric1992
with their project, endorse them, and credit them if you be so kind, i've used Veeblix-Images and have rearranged them
in different layers to get a sunsprite which matches my taste and experience much more. The psd is for resizing and mixing,
tga is much darker and has more contrast (if you wonder while they differ).

the .ini-file resides in .../Skyrim/enbseries

the .tga-file resides beside your enbsunsprite.fx could be .../Skyrim/enbseries or .../Skyrim/ it differs from different enb-versions you use.

Permissions:

use it as you like, but dont claim this images / ressources as your own! Please do not reupload on other sites!

Credits:

Veeblix and Kingeric1992
